    },
    {
        title: "03. Types of Hackers",
        content: "<ul><li><strong>White Hat:</strong> Ethical professionals helping organizations.</li><li><strong>Black Hat:</strong> Criminals acting for personal gain.</li><li><strong>Grey Hat:</strong> Individuals who may break laws but without malicious intent.</li></ul>"
