    {
        title: "08. What is Ethical Hacking?",
        content: "<ul><li>The practice of using hacking skills to find and fix security holes.</li><li>Companies hire them to 'test' their own defenses.</li><li>A vital part of modern infrastructure protection.</li></ul>"
    },
    {
        title: "09. Cybersecurity Safety Tips",
        content: "<ul><li>Use strong, unique passwords for every site.</li><li>Enable Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA).</li><li>Keep all software and OS updated.</li><li>Install reputable antivirus/firewall software.</li></ul>"
